Field Detail

RAPDU_OK

public static final int RAPDU_OK
Everything is OK

RAPDU_LE_INCORRECT

public static final int RAPDU_LE_INCORRECT
The response data length is bigger than Le. The length required is given in the LSB of the return code

RAPDU_LC_INCORRECT

public static final int RAPDU_LC_INCORRECT
Lc is incorrect. The maximum allowable value for Lc or the incorrect Lc submitted in the previos command is given in the LSB

RAPDU_KEY_STATUS_NOT_FULFILLED

public static final int RAPDU_KEY_STATUS_NOT_FULFILLED
The key status was not fulfilled. Key is incomplete, has been invalidated or is not verified.

RAPDU_KEY_CONDITIONS_OF_USE_NOT_SATISFIED

public static final int RAPDU_KEY_CONDITIONS_OF_USE_NOT_SATISFIED
The condition of use is not satisfied. The key is a hash key

RAPDU_KEY_USAGE_ERROR

public static final int RAPDU_KEY_USAGE_ERROR
Key usage error: the key used is not allowed

RAPDU_FUNCTION_NOT_SUPPORTED

public static final int RAPDU_FUNCTION_NOT_SUPPORTED
This function is not supported. The PKA algorithm or padding algorithm is not supported by the card.
